<%@ Control Language="C#" Inherits="System.Web.Mvc.ViewUserControl<ClientSiteViewData>" %>
<%@ Import Namespace="Dtm.Framework.ClientSites" %>

<link rel="stylesheet" href="/css/product-details.css">

<div class="product-details modal__stage">
    <button data-modal-action="close" class="product-details__close modal__close"></button>
    <article id="product-detail-0" class="product-details__article product-details__article--is-visible">
        <h3>Echo Show 5 with Alexa</h3>
        <ul>
            <li>Echo Show 5 connects to Alexa to give you vivid visuals on a 5.5" screen with a crisp full sound&mdash;all in a compact design that fits in any room, in any home</li>
            <li>Voice control compatible devices or manage them on the easy-to-use display. Ask Alexa to show you security cameras, control lights, and adjust thermostats.</li>
            <li>Cook along to step-by-step recipes. Easily update to-do lists and calendars. Glance at weather and traffic on your way out.</li>
            <li>Ask Alexa to show you movie trailers, TV shows, movies, or the news. Or listen to radio stations, podcasts, and audiobooks.</li>
            <li>Designed to protect your privacy &ndash; Turn off the microphone and camera with one press of a button. Slide the built-in shutter to cover the camera.</li>
        </ul>
    </article>
    <article id="product-detail-1" class="product-details__article">
        <h3>Ring Indoor Camera</h3>
        <ul>
            <li>Compact, yet powerful plug-in indoor security camera</li>
            <li>See, hear and speak to people and pets from your phone, tablet, or select Echo device.</li>
            <li>Easily setup your Indoor Camera by plugging into a standard outlet and connecting to Wi-Fi.</li>
            <li>Place on a flat surface or mount to a wall with the versatile mounting bracket.</li>
        </ul>
    </article>
    <article id="product-detail-2" class="product-details__article">
        <h3>Two Philips Hue Smart Lights</h3>
        <ul>
            <li>Set the mood with 50,000 shades of tunable white light.</li>
            <li>Control your Philips Hue Smart Lights all with just the touch of a button on your mobile device or by just asking Alexa.</li>
            <li>Add up to 10 Hue Bluetooth/Zigbee smart bulbs with the (free) Hue Bluetooth app.</li>
            <li>Create timers and routines to automate your entire smart home lighting setup.</li>
        </ul>
    </article>
    <article id="product-detail-3" class="product-details__article">
        <h3>Amazon Smart Plug</h3>
        <ul>
            <li>Add voice control to any outlet.</li>
            <li>Schedule lights, fans, and appliances to turn on and off automatically, or control them remotely when you're away.</li>
            <li>Compact design keeps your second outlet free.</li>
            <li>No smart home hub required&mdash;set up routines and schedules through the Alexa app.</li>
        </ul>
    </article>
</div>